0California.%20It%20provides%20companies%20with%20software-defined%20networking%2C%20cloud%2C%20and%20security%20solutions.%20Founded%20in%201984%2C%20Cisco%20has%20nearly%2085%2C000%20employees%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223af4b631-ce4a-482b-b4c4-eee146d27df0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20analysis%3A%20What%20problem%20were%20they%20trying%20to%20solve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrancine%20Katsoudas%2C%20a%20Cisco%20executive%20vice%20president%20and%20its%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company's%20success%20was%20due%20to%20its%20people.%20But%20ensuring%20the%20company%20is%20recruiting%20the%20best%20can%20be%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20candidates%20need%20to%20be%20persuaded%20to%20apply.%20Connecting%20with%20these%20so-called%20quiet%20candidates%20was%20an%20early%20use%20case%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20at%20Cisco%2C%20Katsoudas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20you%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20quiet%20candidate%20has%20always%20been%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20an%20art%2C%26quot%3B%20Katsoudas%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%2C%20I%20hear%20from%20candidates%20who%20say%2C%20'I%20never%20responded%20to%20an%20email.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20respond%20to%20this%20email%20from%20this%20recruiter.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Francine%20Katsoudas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6646330314fb5b23cc5d3951%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrancine%20Katsoudas%2C%20a%20Cisco%20executive%20vice%20president%20and%20its%20chief%20people%20officer.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cisco%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKatsoudas%20said%20a%20skilled%20recruiter%20could%20find%20the%20right%20combination%20of%20words%20to%20persuade%20candidates%20to%20pay%20attention.%20Good%20recruiters%20personalize%20emails%2C%20but%20honing%20the%20right%20message%20can%20take%20time.%20AI%20can%20help%20speed%20up%20the%20process%2C%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20learned%20is%20that%20you%20can%20be%20so%20much%20more%20customized%20via%20AI%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Katsoudas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3cf2d12-27c1-409c-b92f-616d9a187a34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20Katsoudas%2C%20Zohra%20Yafai%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20talent%20acquisition%20at%20Cisco%2C%20worked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-help-recruit-hire-employees-tech-women-bias-job-seeking-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintegrate%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20recruitment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERandstad%2C%20a%20global%20human-resources%20firm%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20Cisco%20works%20with%20for%20staffing.%20Their%20experimentations%20with%20AI%20in%20recruitment%20helped%20make%20Cisco%20feel%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20more%20confident%20and%20bold%2C%26quot%3B%20Katsoudas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd30701-463a-4b66-b855-30c65acda283%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20uses%20generative%20AI%20to%20help%20gather%20information%20about%20a%20hiring%20target%20and%20to%20customize%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-email-inbox-revolution-chatgpt-google-openai-shortwave-productivity-tools-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemails%20it%20sends%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20tailoring%20its%20recruiting%20messages%2C%20Cisco%20can%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20emails%20it%20sends%20to%20quiet%20candidates%20who%20might%20resist%20other%20forms%20of%20connection.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20can%20increase%20the%20return%20on%20these%20emails%20that%20your%20recruiters%20send%20out%2C%20that%20is%20meaningful%2C%26quot%3B%20Katsoudas%20said.%20The%20company%20started%20slowly%20before%20ramping%20up%20its%20efforts%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20we're%20doing%2C%20we%20probably%20start%20with%20an%20experiment%20or%20a%20pilot%20where%20we're%20running%20analytics%20and%20understanding%20any%20risks%20before%20we%20move%20forward%20and%20set%20our%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20is%20also%20using%20AI%20to%20schedule%20the%20interviews%20and%20meetings%20that%20follow.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20we%20would%20manually%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20Katsoudas%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20can%20do%20all%20that%20via%20AI%2C%20it's%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220de6e3ad-c6e8-47ff-8ec6-6585acb0a367%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpeed%20is%20important%20in%20the%20hiring%20process.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20company%20is%20coming%20after%20you%2C%20and%20they're%20moving%20quickly%2C%20there's%20something%20really%20positive%20in%20that%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20company%20reaches%20out%2C%20and%20then%20you%20don't%20hear%20for%2C%20like%2C%20three%20or%20four%20weeks%2C%20and%20then%20the%20meeting%20gets%20scheduled%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20there%20isn't%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20that%20you're%20demonstrating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20said%20its%20adoption%20of%20AI%20was%20still%20in%20the%20early%20stages%2C%20so%20it%20hadn't%20identified%20quantitative%20markers%20of%20success.%20But%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20continue%20to%20monitor%20progress%20and%20evaluate%20areas%20of%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4d229de-dd5e-4f39-a8e3-614603378b84%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKatsoudas%20said%20more%20pilot%20projects%20would%20be%20rolled%20out%20to%20test%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https