005_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Stop%20harassing%20my%20old%20and%20ailing%20parents'%3A%20Kejriwal%20tells%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716463178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110366035%2Cimgsize-32334.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fstop-harassing-my-old-and-sick-parents-delhi-cm-kejriwal-tells-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F110365859.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fstop-harassing-my-old-and-sick-parents-delhi-cm-kejriwal-tells-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F110365859.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Teen's%20Porsche%20Crash%20Puts%20Spotlight%20On%20Supari%20Case%20Against%20Grandfather%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20driver%2C%20whose%20drunken%20drive%20in%20a%20Porsche%20Taycan%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20software%20engineers%20dead%20in%20Pune%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20crash.%20The%20bail%20order%20says%20he%20was%20being%20released%20on%20the%20assurance%20of%20his%20grandfather%20that%20he%20will%20keep%20the%20teen%20away%20from%20%26quot%3Bbad%20company%26quot%3B.%20It%20has%20now%20emerged%20that%20the%20grandfather%2C%20who%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20started%20the%20family's%20real%20estate%20business%2C%20has%20links%20with%20gangster%20Rajendra%20Sadashiv%20Nikalje%2C%20widely%20known%20as%20Chhota%20Rajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20dates%20back%20to%20a%202009%20attack%20on%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20corporarator%20Ajay%20Bhosale.%20According%20to%20the%20CBI%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20boy's%20grandfather%20was%20locked%20in%20a%20property%20dispute%20with%20his%20brother%20and%20had%20allegedly%20contacted%20Chhota%20Rajan%20to%20mediate.%20The%20gangster%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Shiv%20Sena%20corporator%20Ajay%20Bhosale%2C%20who%20knew%20the%20brother.%20But%20Mr%20Bhosale%20was%20busy%20with%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20that%20year%20and%20refused%20to%20intervene.%20The%20boy's%20grandfather%20suspected%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20was%20backing%20his%20brother%20and%20allegedly%20asked%20Chhota%20Rajan%20to%20bump%20him%20off%2C%20the%20CBI%20chargesheet%20said.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader's%20car%20was%20fired%20at%20near%20Pune's%20Koregaon%20Park%2C%20but%20bullet%20missed%20him%20and%20hit%20his%20driver%20instead%2C%20injuring%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhosale%2C%20who%20is%20now%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20his%20'supari'%20was%20given%20by%20the%20builder%2C%20who%20is%20not%20being%20named%20because%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Porsche%20case%20is%20a%20minor.%20The%20grandfather%20was%20also%20listed%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20but%20not%20arrested.%20The%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case%20is%20now%20part%20of%20a%20bunch%20of%20cases%20against%20Chhota%20Rajan%20pending%20before%20a%20Mumbai%20CBI%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20back%20then%20too%2C%20Pune%20Police%20had%20faced%20questions%20regarding%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case.%20Significantly%2C%20despite%20an%20underworld%20connection%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20was%20not%20invoked%20in%20the%20case%20and%20only%20IPC%20sections%20were%20invoked.%20In%20the%20FIR%20registered%20at%20Bund%20Garden%20police%20station%2C%20the%20builder%20grandfather%20was%20not%20named.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20that%20he%20came%20under%20the%20radar%20and%20was%20named%20an%20accused.%20But%20while%20most%20other%20accused%20were%20arrested%2C%20he%20secured%20an%20anticipatory%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20outrage%20over%20the%20software%20engineers'%20deaths%20and%2