t%20months.%20But%20Ravizza%20said%20most%20of%20his%20clients%20use%20the%20vans%20for%20traveling%20or%20for%20%26quot%3Bweekend%20getaways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20enjoyed%20making%20and%20building%20things%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Ravizza%20said%20his%20interest%20in%20vans%20didn't%20begin%20until%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20realized%20building%20his%20own%20van%20would%20be%20a%20safe%20way%20to%20travel%20the%20US%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20He%20spent%20time%20researching%20how%20to%20build%20and%20design%20vans%2C%20watching%20YouTube%20videos%2C%20and%20connecting%20with%20experienced%20van%20builders%2C%20who%20showed%20him%20the%20ropes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recently%20spent%20eight%20months%20renovating%20a%20Mercedes%202022%20Sprinter%20170%26quot%3B%204%C3%974%20with%20self-heating%20lithium%20batteries%2C%20custom%20walnut%20flooring%2C%20a%20walk-in%20shower%2C%20and%20smart-tinted%20glass%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20van%2C%20which%20can%20host%20six%20people%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ravizzaluxuryvans.com%2Forder%3Futm_source%3Dhoobe%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20market%20for%20%24295%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavizza%20said%20anyone%20can%20upgrade%20a%20van%20to%20add%20luxury%20elements%2C%20but%20there's%20one%20mistake%20they%20should%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237a0eaf3-8950-4cb6-b143-691b38abca71%5C%22%3ECutting%20costs%20with%20cheap%20material%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERavizza%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20said%20the%20biggest%20mistake%20he%20sees%20people%20make%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20knowing%20which%20materials%20to%20use%20and%20which%20tools%20to%20use%2C%20and%20how%20to%20use%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20as%20simple%20as%20not%20knowing%20what%20a%20pocket%20hole%20is%20can%20change%20the%20look%20and%20structure%20of%20your%20whole%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22luxury%20van%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633aa9aec0c696569002773%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cabinets%20in%20the%20van%20were%20designed%20with%20smart-tinted%20glass.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Malone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERavizza%20said%20you%20should%20also%20be%20willing%20to%20dedicate%20the%20time%20(every%20van%20he%20designs%20takes%20around%20eight%20months%20to%20complete)%20and%20the%20funds%20to%20source%20the%20highest%20quality%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavizza%20said%20each%20van%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%2490%2C000%20to%20purchase%2C%20and%20the%20materials%20usually%20cost%20a%20further%20%2490%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20aesthetics%2C%20to%20get%20that%20feeling%2C%20you%20need%20to%20research%20materials%20and%20figure%20out%20what%20are%20the%20nice%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere's%20one%20example%3A%20The%20laminate%20I%20use%20in%20my%20van%20is%20%24350%20per%20sheet%20when%20compared%20to%20laminate%20that%20I%20can%20go%20buy%20for%20%2450%20per%20sheet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavizza%20said%20he%20used%20Italian%20tiles%20for%20the%20shower%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20four%20times%20as%20much%20as%20they%20needed%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%20Elsewhere%20in%20the%20van%2C%20he%20said%20he%20used%20real%20walnut%20hardwood%20which%20cost%20around%20%244%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20would%20be%20a%20little%20scared%20of%20the%20price%20of%20wood%2C%20that's%20just%20an%20aesthetic%20and%20serves%20no%20other%20function%2C%20but%20that%20right%20there%20is%20what%20changes%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20you%20shouldn't%20sacrifice%20any%20of%20the%20smaller%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20also%20you%20do%20have%20to%20be%20a%20little%20obsessed%20and%20passionate%2C%26quot%3B%20Ravizza%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20passionate%20about%20doing%20things%20right%20and%20to%20the%20best%20of%20your%20abilities%20and%20you're%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20little%20extra%20time%2C%20then%20just%20getting%20into%20each%20little%20corner%20of%20the%20van%20and%20hyper-obsessing%20is%20how%20that%20comes%20to%20fruition%20%E2%80%94%20for%20me%2C%20at%20least.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-van-designer-biggest-mistake-cheaping-out-materials-genz-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716461704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66349b1e0dfb1341e9022a5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-van-designer-biggest-mistake-cheaping-out-materials-genz-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luxury%20van%20life%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20according%20to%20Lucas%20Ravizza%2C%20a%20van%20builder%20who%20creates%20custom%20motorhomes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfriel%40businessinsider.com%20(Mikhaila%20Friel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-van-designer-biggest-mistake-cheaping-out-materials-genz-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%2420%2C000%20Per%20Seat%20For%20IND%20vs%20PAK%20Game%20At%20T20%20WC%3F%20Lalit%20Modi%20Blasts%20ICC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20is%20just%20round%20the%20corner%20and%20the%20cricket%20fans%20all%20around%20the%20world%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20much-anticipated%20clash%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20two%20teams%20have%20not%20played%20a%20bilateral%20series%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20due%20to%20political%20tensions%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20their%20matches