p%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261db667d-5f59-4651-a598-5b034ba75bf8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20kept%20in%20touch%20through%20letters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20then%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%2C%20both%20actors%2C%20traveled%20where%20the%20theatre%20work%20was%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Southeast%20for%20dinner%20theatre%20and%20the%20Northeast%20with%20children's%20theatre.%20At%20least%20weekly%2C%20there%20would%20be%20mail%20from%20Maureen.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvintage-us-postcards-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20postcard%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20her%20own%20travels%20or%20a%20New%20Yorker%20cartoon%20she%20found%20hilarious.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOften%20her%20letters%20were%20entertaining%20descriptions%20of%20her%20life%20%E2%80%94%20waitressing%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-being-lawyer-to-write-and-record-podcasts-no-regrets-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eworking%20at%20a%20law%20firm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Or%20she'd%20tell%20about%20her%20risky%20adventures%2C%20driving%20(usually%20barefoot%20and%20low%20on%20gas)%20well%20after%20midnight%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20stranded%20buddy.%20She%20wrote%20about%20the%20crazy%20crash%20diets%20she%20invented.%20Some%20of%20Mo's%20letters%20were%20on%20company%20letterhead%20(%26quot%3BThe%20boss%20thinks%20I'm%20typing%20up%20a%20brief%2C%20but%20ha!%20I'm%20really%20writing%20to%20you!%26quot%3B).%20Her%20handwritten%20notes%20had%20her%20large%2C%20loopy%20script%20covering%20page%20after%20page.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShortly%20before%20she%20died%2C%20Maureen%20decided%20to%20move%20North.%20We%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphiladelphia-what-to-know-about-visiting-from-a-local-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esettled%20in%20Philadelphia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20then%2C%20and%20she%20was%20eager%20to%20make%20a%20fresh%20start.%20Those%20final%20letters%20were%20filled%20with%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20for%20a%20new%20life%20(%26quot%3BBreak%20me%20into%20Philly!%26quot%3B).%20When%20we%20traveled%20to%20Atlanta%20for%20her%20funeral%2C%20we%20saw%20Mo's%20open%20suitcases%2C%20silent%20reminders%20that%20she%20really%20had%20been%20on%20her%20way%20to%20us%20before%20the%20accident%20that%20ended%20everything%20for%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bc1fafe-cd06-4403-9fc9-22757010dec5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wanted%20my%20kids%20to%20know%20their%20aunt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20my%20five%20kids%20grew%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20describe%20their%20aunt%2C%20but%20my%20words%20always%20fell%20far%20short%20of%20capturing%20her%20personality.%20I%20would%20re-read%20the%20letters%20every%20year%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20her%20death%20and%20cry.%20Why%20didn't%20I%20give%20them%20to%20my%20children%20to%20read%20as%20well%3F%20It%20never%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20right%20moment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decades%20passed.%20I%20finally%20gave%20Maureen's%20robe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-bought-roman-bust-artifact-goodwill-35-dollars-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20Goodwill%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Her%20cologne%20turned%20rancid%20and%20was%20thrown%20away.%20There%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20when%20I%20shared%20a%20few%20letters%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20they%20remained%20in%20a%20box.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%202021%20marked%2040%20years%20since%20my%20sister's%20death.%20Walking%20with%20a%20friend%20one%20day%2C%20I%20mentioned%20the%20letters%2C%20and%20she%20suggested%20I%20have%20them%20photocopied.%20Finally%2C%20there%20was%20a%20plan%20to%20preserve%20them%20and%20make%20a%20bound%20copy%20for%20each%20of%20my%20children.%20My%20friend%20helped%20accomplish%20this%20task%2C%20and%20now%20I%20had%20a%20precious%20gift%20to%20give%20the%20kids.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20I%20gave%20them%20their%20books%20(my%20children%20were%20all%20grown%20now%20and%20living%20in%20various%20cities).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20bug%20them%20about%20reading%20the%20letters%20or%20quiz%20them%20about%20their%20reactions.%20It's%20up%20to%20them%20to%20decide%20how%20and%20when%20they%20read%20them.%20But%20I'm%20very%20glad%20they%20have%20these%20snapshots%20of%20Mo's%20life.%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20this%20history%20of%20my%20beloved%20sister%2C%20in%20her%20own%20words.%20She%20shines%20through%20every%20sentence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20I%20believe%2C%20through%20the%20letters%2C%20Maureen%20lives%20on%2C%20not%20just%20for%20me%2C%20but%20for%20the%20nieces%20and%20nephews%20she%20would%20have%20loved%20so%20much%20but%20never%20got%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdead-sisters-letters-kids-connection-aunt-2023-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716460261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664bb7679fc063e829b30eb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdead-sisters-letters-kids-connection-aunt-2023-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20sister%20died%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20when%20she%20was%2023.%20I%20kept%20all%20her%20letters%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20my%20children%20so%20they%20could%20have%20a%20connection%20with%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elise%20Seyfried)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdead-sisters-letters-kids-connection-aunt-2023-5%22%2C%22cdn