2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markles-favourite-workout-megaformer-how-to-get-results-at-home-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMegaformer%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fitness%20machine%20akin%20to%20a%20Pilates%20reformer%2C%20but%20souped%20up.%20Created%20by%20trainer%20to%20the%20stars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-trainer-said-mirror-is-good-fitness-trend-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESebastien%20Lagree%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20patented%20in%202006%2C%20the%20Megaformer%20uses%20spring-based%20resistance%20to%20challenge%20the%20body%20with%20plenty%20of%20time%20under%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20Lagree's%20celebrity%20fans%20is%20long%2C%20including%2C%20reportedly%2C%20Jennifer%20Aniston%2C%20Meghan%20Markle%2C%20Kate%20Hudson%2C%20Jennifer%20Lopez%2C%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20and%20Kim%20Kardashian.%20The%20workouts%20started%20in%20the%20US%20but%20are%20now%20available%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20the%20industry%20of%20boutique%20fitness%20studios%20is%20booming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kim%20Kardashian%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e19b79fc063e829b3acb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKim%20Kardashian%20in%20April%202024.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Granitz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20boutique%20fitness%20studio%20market%20is%20currently%20valued%20at%20%2455.16%20billion%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20%2479.66%20billion%20in%202029%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchandmarkets.com%2Freport%2Fboutique-fitness-studio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20and%20Markets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20big%20UK%20cities%2C%20at%20least%2C%20demand%20for%20luxurious%20ways%20to%20workout%20is%20staying%20strong%20despite%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20health%20and%20fitness%20reporter%2C%20and%20I%20exercise%20most%20days%20a%20week%20doing%20both%20a%20mix%20of%20strength%20and%20cardio%20workouts%2C%20but%20the%20Megaformer%20was%20tough.%20While%20I've%20done%20reformer%20pilates%20before%20and%20used%20to%20do%20lots%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbarre-workout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebarre%3C%2Fa%3E%20classes%2C%20I%20haven't%20done%20any%20low-impact%20high-intensity%20workouts%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoing-pilates-for-20-years-strengthened-body-throughout-life-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPilates%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20since%20I%20moved%20out%20of%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burn%20was%20real%20and%20my%20inner%20thighs%20felt%20it%20in%20the%20days%20afterward%2C%20and%2C%20seeing%20as%20I%20don't%20normally%20do%20Pilates-style%20workouts%2C%20the%20class%20reminded%20me%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20vary%20your%20training%20for%20overall%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b174c06-a6e9-4a10-8062-9e1004d5e682%5C%22%3EThe%20gym%20was%20luxurious%20but%20minimalist%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20club-style%20studios%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20fitness%20studios%20in%20London%20offering%20Megaformer%20workout%20classes%20now%2C%20both%20at%20%C2%A335%20(%2445).%20I%20went%20to%20Studio%20Fix%20in%20Kensington%20%E2%80%94%20an%20affluent%20area%20that%20has%20no%20shortage%20of%20bougie%20boutique%20gyms%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20gym's%20other%20classes%20cost%20%C2%A325%20(%2432).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entrance%20has%20a%20minimalist%2C%20modern%2C%20and%20industrial%20interior%20(think%20exposed%20pipes%20on%20the%20ceiling)%20with%20gold%20and%20chrome%20accents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Studio%20Fix%20entrance%20and%20reception%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e15ef9fc063e829b3aa9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Studio%20Fix%20entrance%20and%20reception%20area.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20checked%20in%20for%20my%20class%20at%20the%20reception%20and%20glanced%20at%20the%20protein%20shake%20menu.%20%C2%A37.50%20(%249.50)%20each...%20Perhaps%20a%20luxury%20I%20could%20go%20without.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changing%20room%20had%20Dyson%20hair%20dryers%20and%20straighteners%2C%20deodorant%2C%20dry%20shampoo%2C%20hair%20spray%2C%20and%20hair%20ties%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floreal-aesop-skincare-brand-luxury-aspirational-millennial-deal-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAesop%3C%2Fa%3E%20toiletries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Studio%20Fix%20changing%20room%20and%20showers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e167e20abc1efe8fc6573%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Studio%20Fix%20changing%20room%20and%20showers.%3Cp%3ESauce%20Communications%2FRachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20other%20light%2C%20bright%20studios%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20the%20Megaformer%20studio%20is%20decked%20out%20in%20mirrors%20and%20red%20lights%20with%20no%20windows%2C%20creating%20a%20club-style%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Studio%20Fix's%20Megaformer%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e154414fb5b23cc5f1dab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudio%20Fix's%20Megaformer%20studio.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20machines%20look%20pretty%20daunting%3A%20They're%20huge%2C%20with%20various%20handles%20and%20straps%20and%20a%20moving%20%26quot%3Bcarriage%26quot%3B%20with%20different%20markings%20that%20slides%20forward%20and%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20there%20early%20so%20the%20class%20instructor%2C%20Andrea%2C%20could%20talk%20me%20and%20the%20other%20newbies%20through%20the%20basics.%20She%20told%20me%20and%20my%20five%20classmates%20(glossy%2C%20slim%20women%20in%20their%2030s%20and%2040s)%20we%20might%20find%20it%20hard%20on%20our%20first%20attempt.%20And%20she%20was%20not%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bdc2525-01d2-420c-b2a0-26d2c7c07ee3%5C%22%3EIt's%20all%20about%20time%20under%20tension%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class%20started%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkatrin-davidsdottir-best-ab-exercises-strengthen-core-deadbugs-planks-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecore%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20at%20first%2C%20it%20felt%20pretty%20manageable.%20But%20that%20core%20work%20went%20on%2C%20and%20on%2C%20and%20as%20it%20did%2C%20my%20abs%20fast%20began%20to%20burn%20and%20fatigue.%20There%20were%20pikes%2C%20planks%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20pulses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMegaformer%20workouts%20feature%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20movements%20as%20well%20as%20bigger%20ones%20with%20a%20larger%20range%20of%20motion%2C%20and%20you're%20meant%20to%20do%20each%20movement%20super%20slowly%20(think%20four%20seconds%20down%20in%20a%20lunge%20and%20four%20back%20up)%20to%20maximize%20time%20under%20tension.%20It%20sounds%20easy.%20It%20was%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222718%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20sitting%20on%20the%20Megaformer%20before%20the%20class%20began.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e170d14fb5b23cc5f1ebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222039%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20sitting%20on%20the%20Megaformer%20before%20the%20class%20began.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Lagree%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincreasing-time-under-tension-working-out-slower-secret-results-gym-sebastien-lagree-personal-trainer-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20moving%20slowly%20means%20you%20can't%20employ%20momentum%20to%20lift%20a%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20get%20a%20better%20response%20from%20working%20out%20because%20you%20will%20activate%20more%20muscle%20fibers.%20When%20you're%20just%20using%20explosive%20movements%2C%20you're%20only%20activating%20mostly%20the%20fast-twitch%20muscle%20fibers%2C%20which%20are%20responsible%20for%20building%20bulk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrea%20shouted%20instructions%20and%20demonstrated%20each%20movement%20throughout%20the%20class%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20didn't%20feel%20clueless.%20I%20welcomed%20any%20breaks%20she%20took%20to%20demonstrate%20each%20movement%20first%2C%20otherwise%20there'd%20have%20been%20zero%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20core%20section%20was%20over%2C%20we%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20lower%20body%20and%20performed%20a%20range%20of%20exercises%20on%20one%20side%20using%20the%20straps%20and%20cables%20before%20repeating%20on%20the%20other.%20We%20never%20had%20to%20do%20any%20one%20exercise%20for%20too%20long%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20plenty%20long%20enough%20to%20burn.%20Many%20of%20the%20exercises%20looked%20easy%2C%20but%20were%20surprisingly%20painful%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20good%20way%3A%20my%20muscles%20were%20burning%20and%20began%20to%20shake%20as%20I%20worked%20them%20in%20ways%20I%20wasn't%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20section%20of%20the%20workout%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-exercises-build-upper-body-muscle-short-time-gym-workout-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupper%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20easiest%20and%20the%20shortest%2C%20and%20I'd%20have%20liked%20it%20to%20be%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dca72a1d-a36f-43c3-ae44-596aa0fef6fc%5C%22%3EThe%20class%20was%20too%20expensive%20for%20me%20to%20do%20regularly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class%20went%20by%20quickly.%20Afterward%20I%20felt%20proud%20of%20myself%20and%20my%20body%20felt%20good%20from%20the%20stretching%20and%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20afternoon%20and%20the%20days%20following%2C%20the%20body%20part%20where%20I%20really%20felt%20sore%20was%20the%20inner%20thighs%2C%20which%20reminded%20me%20that%20I%20mustn't%20neglect%20them%20in%20my%20own%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Hosie%20at%20Studio%20Fix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e17ac14fb5b23cc5f1efe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20before%20the%20class%20and%20the%20waiting%20area%20outside%20the%20studios.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20a%20good%20reminder%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20variety%20in%20exercise.%20You%20can%20be%20squatting%20twice%20your%20bodyweight%20but%20unable%20to%20pulse%20in%20a%20lunge%20on%20a%20Megaformer%20for%2015%20seconds%20if%20you%20never%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20do%20solely%20Megaformer%20classes%2C%20as%20it's%20important%20to%20do%20heavier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-women-benefits-lift-weights-celebrity-personal-trainer-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cardio%20too%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20my%20workout%20regime%20if%20my%20budget%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Studio%20Fix%20founder%20Najeeb%20Abunahl%20why%20the%20Megaformer%20workouts%20cost%20more%20than%20others%20at%20the%20studio%2C%20he%20told%20me%20it%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20licensing%20agreement%20they%20have%20with%20Sebastian%20Lagree%20to%20use%20and%20train%20on%20Megaformers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20bring%20a%20Master%20Trainer%20from%20Europe%20to%20certify%20all%20of%20our%20instructors%20in%20the%20Lagree%20method%2C%26quot%3B%20Abunahl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20me%2C%20the%20price%20tag%20is%20just%20too%20high.%20But%20if%20I%20had%20cash%20to%20splash%2C%20I'd%20go%20back%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flagree-megaformer-workout-review-pilates-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716457262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e1a3a14fb5b23cc5f1ffd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flagree-megaformer-workout-review-pilates-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Megaformer%20class%2C%20in%20affluent%20West%20London%2C%20took%20place%20in%20a%20dark%20studio%20illuminated%20by%20red%20lights.%20I%20work%20out%20most%20days%2C%20but%20my%20thighs%20were%20burning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flagree-megaformer-workout-review-pilates-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Teen%20Porsche%20Driver's%20Grandfather%20Called%20For%20Questioning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20grandfather%20of%20the%2017-year-old%20Pune%20boy%2C%20who%20rammed%20his%20father's%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20Porsche%20car%20into%20two%20people%2C%20was%20on%20Thursday%20called%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grandfather%20is%20currently%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20Pune%20crime%20branch%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20in%20Pune%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Porsche%20car%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20the%20teenager%20when%20he%20was%20drunk%2C%20fatally%20knocked%20down%20the%20two%20software%20engineers%20on%20a%20bike%20in%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday.%20But%2C%20fifteen%20hours%20after%20the%20late-night%20crash%2C%20he%20was%20released%20on%20bail%2C%20which%20listed%20conditions%20like%20writing%20an%20essay%20on%20road%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20public%20outcry%20over%20quick%20bail%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20child%20observation%20home%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeen%20Porsche%20Driver%20Got%20Bail%20On%20Grandfather's%20Assurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board's%20order%20listed%20seven%20conditions%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20bail%20for%20the%20teen%2C%20whom%20the%20police%20want%20to%20charge%20as%20an%20adult%20given%20the%20%26quot%3Bheinous%26quot%3B%20nature%20of%20the%20crime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bail%20order%2C%20the%20board%20said%20that%20the%20boy's%20grandfather%20has%20given%20%26quot%3Bassurance%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20will%20keep%20him%20away%20from%20%26quot%3Bany%20bad%20company%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20writing%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20%26quot%3Broad%20accidents%20and%20their%20solutions%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20was%20released%20on%20two%20bonds%20of%20Rs%207%2C500%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20bail%20conditions%20were%20also%20imposed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E...%20will%20visit%20the%20RTO%20(regional%20transport%20office)%20and%20study%20all%20rules%20and%20regulations%2C%20present%20a%20presentation%2C%20and%20submit%20the%20same%20to%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20within%2015%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E...%20will%20assist%20RTO%20officials%20and%20study%20traffic%20rules%20for%2015%20days%2C%20and%20submit%20a%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E...%20will%20be%20referred%20to%20external%20de-addiction%20counselling%20(for%20alcohol%20consumption).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E...%20will%20consult%20psychiatrics%20at%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20(a%20government%20medical%20facility)%2C%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20within%2015%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E...%20parent%20of%20CCL%20(child%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law)%20is%20directed%20to%20keep%20him%20present%20before%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20as%20and%20when%20required%2C%20and%20keep%20him%20away%20from%20'bad%20company'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20illegally%20driving%20the%20Porsche%20(he%20is%20four%20months%20shy%20of%2018%2C%20the%20minimum%20legal%20age%20to%20drive%20a%20car)%2C%20the%20boy%20and%20his%20friends%20were%20served%20alcohol%20by%20a%20city%20establishment%2C%20identified%20as%20Cosie%20Bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20and%20the%20boy's%20father%20have%20both%20been%20charged%3B%20they%20face%20police%20cases%20under%20Sections%2075%20and%2077%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20wilful%20neglect%20of%20a%20child%20and%20providing%20liquor%20and%2For%20narcotics%20to%20an%20underage%20person%2C%20unless%20prescribed%20by%20a%20medical%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716457140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-teen-porsche-drivers-grandfather-called-for-questioning-5727724%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20grandfather%20of%20the%2017-year-old%20Pune%20boy%2C%20who%20rammed%20his%20father's%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20Porsche%20car%20into%20two%20people%2C%20was%20on%20Thursday%20called%20for%20questioning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%