till%20etched%20in%20global%20memory%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20another%20large-scale%20conflict%20is%20both%20terrifying%20and%20compelling.%20Many%20astrologers%2C%20including%20Nostradamus%20and%20Baba%20Vanga%2C%20have%20made%20predictions%20about%20WW3%20but%20its%20possibility%20remains%20uncertain.%20Still%2C%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20news%20about%20such%20predictions%20keep%20surfacing%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20and%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20in%20this%20series%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bprediction%26quot%3B%20made%20by%20Indian%20astrologer%20Kushal%20Kumar.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20%3Cem%3EMedium%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20he%20has%20also%20shared%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20claimed%20that%20World%20War%203%20is%20just%20weeks%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7199210574319140866%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22457%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fkushal-kumar-9a959832%2F%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20is%20a%20Vedic%20astrologer%2C%20who%20uses%20charts%20that%20show%20planetary%20alignment%20to%20make%20forecast%20about%20future%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2024%20was%20predicted%20to%20be%20majorly%20worrisome%20in%20relation%20to%20war%20conditions%20in%20hotspots%20across%20the%20world%2C%20particularly%20around%20May%208%20-%20it%20was%20indicated%20carrying%20highest%20escalation%20in%20such%20war%20fronts%20as%20Koreas%2C%20China-Taiwan%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20involving%20Israel%20and%20others%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Ukraine-Russia%2C%20anger%20of%20NATO%20could%20also%20find%20expression%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20persons%20charged%20with%20authority%20to%20govern%20in%20some%20countries%20may%20find%20it%20tough%20and%20hard%20to%20cope%20up%20with%20the%20major%20worrisome%20emerging%20scenario.%20Some%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20seriously%20unwell%20or%20may%20even%20resign.%20Upheavals%20in%20the%20political%20scene%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20In%20short%2C%20where%20vulnerable%2C%20the%20contemporary%20planetary%20movements%20suggest%20that%20army%20may%20step%20in%20to%20take%20overall%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20further%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40kushal1948%2Fglobal-fears-of-ww3-being-expressed-in-news-after-death-of-former-iranian-president-ebrahim-raisi-a0da837f7fba%5C%22%3Ein%20his%20post%20on%20%3Cem%3EMedium%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astrologer%20then%20revealed%20the%20date%20he%20thinks%20a%20global%20war%20will%20break%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20Tuesday%2C%2018%20June%202024%20has%20the%20strongest%20planetary%20stimulus%20to%20trigger%20WW3%20although%2010%20and%2029%20June%20may%20have%20a%20say%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanchkula-based%20Mr%20Kumar%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20astrologer%20who%20predicts%20world%20event.%20And%20this%20is%20why%2C%20the%20news%20is%20gaining%20traction%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claims%20come%20just%20days%20after%20UK%20officials%20launched%20a%20website%20to%20tell%20Brits%20what%20they%20need%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20in%20the%20event%20of%20war%20actually%20breaking%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716455100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feb0iog3o_world-war-3-generic_625x300_23_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Findian-astrologer-predicts-exact-date-world-war-3-will-start-5727470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20many%20scenarios%20have%20been%20proposed%20by%20analysts%2C%20futurists%2C%20and%20political