Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fchina-builds-ai-chatbot-trained-on-xi-jinpings-thoughts-heres-all-that-it-can-do%2Farticleshow%2F110360242.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20launches%20a%20new%20chatbot%20based%20on%20Xi%20Jinping's%20political%20philosophy.%20The%20large%20language%20model%20(LLM)%20by%20the%20China%20Cyberspace%20Research%20Institute%20is%20trained%20on%20'Xi%20Jinping%20Thought%20on%20Socialism%20with%20Chinese%20Characteristics%20for%20a%20New%20Era'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fchina-builds-ai-chatbot-trained-on-xi-jinpings-thoughts-heres-all-that-it-can-do%2Farticleshow%2F110360242.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Investigators%20Turned%20Scamsters%3A%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Nursing%20Scam%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20team%20from%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20over%20the%20investigation%20into%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20nursing%20colleges%20scam%20after%20members%20of%20the%20agency's%20earlier%20team%20allegedly%20became%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20Four%20CBI%20officers%2C%20including%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent-rank%20officer%2C%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20three%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20can%20register%20a%20separate%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20against%20the%20officers.%20Also%2C%20the%20colleges%20tagged%20%26quot%3Bsuitable%26quot%3B%20earlier%20could%20be%20re-examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20NDTV%20investigation%20last%20year%20found%20gross%20irregularities%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20nursing%20colleges%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Top%20officials%20in%20the%20health%20education%20department%20were%20found%20running%20nursing%20colleges%20that%20did%20not%20even%20have%20a%20campus.%20Some%20%26quot%3Bcolleges%26quot%3B%20were%20found%20running%20from%20a%20few%20rooms.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20shocking%20revelations%2C%20the%20state%20nursing%20council%20cancelled%20the%20affiliation%20of%2019%20colleges.%20Following%20a%20high%20court%20order%2C%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20started%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20functioning%20of%20670%20colleges%20registered%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20CBI%20Twist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%20on%20308%20nursing%20colleges%2C%20the%20CBI%20tagged%20169%20colleges%20%26quot%3Bfit%26quot%3B%2C%2066%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B%20and%2073%20%26quot%3Bdeficient%26quot%3B.%20But%20there%20were%20questions.%20A%20government%20college%20in%20Rewa%20was%20declared%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20a%20college%20that%20was%20tagged%20%26quot%3Bfit%26quot%3B%20had%20the%20address%20of%20a%20rented%20building%20from%20which%20a%20school%20was%20running.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20CBI%20officers%20were%20providing%20%26quot%3Bfit%26quot%3B%20tags%20in%20exchange%20for%20bribes.%20The%20agency's%20team%20would%20charge%20between%20Rs%202%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20tag%20an%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B%20college%20%26quot%3Bfit%26quot%3B.%20The%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20bribery%20cartel%20functioned%20through%20Rajasthan.%20A%20middleman%20would%20send%20the%20bribes%20to%20Jaipur%20and%20it%20would%20then%20be%20routed%20to%20a%20CBI%20officer%2C%20the%20probe%20has%20found.%20CBI%20officers%20Rahul%20Raj%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Majoka%20and%20Rishi%20Kant%20Asathe%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Deputy%20SP%20Ashish%20Prasad%20is%20also%20an%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20searched%2031%20locations%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Jaipur%20and%20found%20over%20Rs%202.3%20crore%20in%20cash%2C%204%20gold%20bars%20and%20incriminating%20documents.%20Rahul%20Raj%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%2C%20would%20coordinate%20with%20middlemen%20and%20share%20schedule%20of%20CBI%20inspections%2C%20fix%20and%20collect%20bribe%20amounts%2C%20and%20provide%20suitability%20report.%20He%20was%20caught%20red-handed%20while%20accepting%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20as%20bribe%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20Rahul%20Raj%20has%20now%20been%20terminated%20from%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECodewords%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BChaach%20Glass%3A%2C%20%26quot%3BAchar%20Ki%20Barni%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BKilo%20Aam%26quot%3B%20were%20used%20to%20relay%20messages%20about%20bribe%20amounts%20and%20their%20collection%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rule%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gross%20irregularities%20coming%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20nursing%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20state%20government's%20guidelines%20for%20such%20institutions%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Earlier%2C%20such%20a%20college%20could%20only%20function%20if%20it%20had%20an%20area%20of%20at%20least%2023%2C000%20square%20feet.%20This%20minimum%20area%20requirement%20was%20reduced%20to%208%2C000%20square%20feet.%20Also%2C%20the%2010%3A1%20ratio%20of%20assistant%20professor%20and%20students%20was%20tweaked%20to%2020%3A1.%20The%20minimum%20area%20for%20a%20nursing%20lab%20was%20revised%20from%201500%20square%20metres%20to%20900%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV's%20investigation%20had%20earlier%20found%20that%20many%20nursing%20colleges%20were%20running%20without%20proper%20faculty%20or%20infrastructure.%20One%20faculty%20member%20was%20found%20teaching%20in%20at%20least%2010%20colleges%20across%20three%20cities%20--%20as%20principal%20in%20some%20and%20associate%20professor%20in%20others.%20NDTV%20also%20found%20colleges%20that%20have%20no%20faculty%20hand%20out%20%26quot%3B