ted%20to%20have%20a%20discussion%20and%20the%20man%20casually%20mentioned%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F37260%2Fdifferently-abled-friendly-polling-stations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20and%20vote%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyou%20will%20have%20to%20give%20me%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20he%20was%20joking%20but%20I%20readily%20agreed%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20vote.%20He%20did%20show%20up%20some%20hours%20later%20with%20an%20inked%20finger.%20I%20gave%20him%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20juice%20that%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnaraj%20kept%20replaying%20the%20incident%20and%20realised%20that%20there%20must%20be%20many%20more%20people%20like%20that%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20patriot%20and%20have%20wanted%20to%20do%20my%20part%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20growth.%20In%20society%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20highest%20entity%20and%20everyone%20should%20follow%20it.%20The%20incident%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnaraj%20decided%20to%20distribute%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eevery%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInk%20that%20finger%20and%20get%20a%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E!%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20the%202018%20elections%20but%20little%20did%20he%20know%20that%20a%20fight%20lay%20before%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20issued%20a%20notice%20on%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20local%20newspapers%20and%20to%20my%20friends%20that%20I%20will%20be%20distributing%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20whoever%20votes.%20I%20had%20my%20staff%20prepare%20the%20batter%2C%20the%20chutneys%20and%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20found%20out%20that%20he%20was%20barred%20by%20the%20EC%20to%20distribute%20the%20food.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20friend%20advised%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20high%20court%20and%20file%20a%20plea.%20The%20HC%20gave%20a%20verdict%20at%208%3A30%20pm%20in%20my%20favour.%20It%20was%20a%20single-bench%20decision%20but%20it%20was%20challenged%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20hotels%20in%20the%20city.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20another%20hearing%20that%20started%20at%2012%3A30%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20double%20bench%20also%20decided%20that%20my%20cause%20was%20valuable%20and%20I%20could%20do%20it.%20For%20a%20moment%2C%20before%20the%20verdict%2C%20I%20had%20lost%20faith%20and%20was%20worried%20about%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F193325%2Fhyderabad-startup-health-vaccine-food-waste-iot-block-chain-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20wastage%20of%20food%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20it%20would%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nisarga%20Grand%20Hotel%20in%20Bengaluru.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1-1716358248