20idlis.%20Image%3A%20M%20Muthu%20Kannan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Aranthangi%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Pudukottai%20in%201960%20after%20her%20marriage.%20Her%20husband%20used%20to%20run%20a%20tea%20shop%20but%20his%20frail%20health%20meant%20that%20Dhanam%20became%20the%20breadwinner%20of%20the%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20the%20tea%20shop%2C%20she%20ran%20many%20businesses%20to%20support%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20two%20children%2C%20and%20that%20was%20a%20time%20before%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme.%20To%20provide%20for%20their%20clothes%2C%20food%20and%20toys%2C%20I%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20needs%20are%20met%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhanam%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20tea%20shop%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20profitable%2C%20she%20made%20snacks%20too.%20When%20that%20too%20didn%E2%80%99t%20suffice%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%20she%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%201980s.%20Located%20in%20a%20busy%20street%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Pudukkottai%2C%20she%20built%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20of%20everyone%20from%20school%20children%20to%20homemakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20ration%20rice%20and%20pulses%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%20and%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20the%20ration%20items%20she%20gets%20aren%E2%80%99t%20sufficient%20for%20the%20quantity%20she%20makes%2C%20regular%20customers%20and%20well-wishers%20help%20her%20with%20their%20ration%20rice.%20This%20goodwill%20and%20her%20benevolent%20heart%20are%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20her%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%203%20paise%20for%20one%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20less%20than%20other%20hotels%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20everyone%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20principle%20is%20the