turned%20out%20to%20be%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20purchase%20donkeys%2C%20milk%20them%20one%20day%2C%20and%20sell%20their%20milk%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20was%20not%20at%20all%20possible.%20I%20did%20not%20consider%20its%20low%20shelf%20life.%20There%20was%20no%20proper%20local%20market%20for%20it%20and%20it%20could%20not%20be%20sent%20abroad%20in%20its%20liquid%20form%20via%20plane%20or%20ship%20due%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20he%20incurred%20losses%20up%20to%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20as%20he%20had%20to%20throw%203%2C000%20litres%20of%20milk%20down%20the%20drain.%20The%20only%20solution%20was%20to%20transport%20the%20milk%20abroad%20by%20converting%20it%20into%20dry%20powder%20form%20for%20transportation.%20But%20it%20took%20him%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20this%20and%20find%20suitable%20companies%20that%20did%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhiren%20informs%20that%20it%20takes%2017%20litres%20of%20milk%20to%20make%20one%20kg%20powder.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdonkey-milk-1716196367-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDhiren%20informs%20that%20it%20takes%2017%20litres%20of%20milk%20to%20make%20one%20kg%20powder.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20sought%20help%20from%20a%20marketing%20company%20and%20bought%20their%20annual%20package%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20which%20brought%20in%20customers.%20After%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20I%20got%20my%20first%20order%20of%2050%20kg%20milk%20powder%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20time%2C%20Dhiren%20had%20already%20stored%20200%20kg%20of%20milk%20powder.%20He%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%2017%20litres%20of%20milk%20to%20make%20one%20kg%20powder.%20It%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%2063%2C000%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20international%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20Dhiren%20was%20able%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20business%20and%20gradually%20expanded%20his%20farm%20to%2050%20donkeys.%20The%20current%20daily%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255951%2Fhyderabad-sids-farm-iit-kharagpur-cow-cattle-earns-crores-milk-subscription-plan-dairy-revenue-kishore-indukuri-inspirational-success-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20production%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20his%20farm%20is%20about%2015%20litres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20he%20also%20ensures%20the%20general%20well-being%20of%20the%20donkeys%20at%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20donkeys%20are%20not%20exploited%20for%20milk.%20In%20our%20village%2C%20we%20have%20a%20veterinary%20hospital%20very%20close%20to%20our%20farm.%20We%20get%20them%20treated%20and%20vaccinated%20for%20tetanus%20every%20year%20and%20give%20them%20B-complex%20supplements%20every%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20success%2C%20Dhiren%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20work%2C%20I%20feel%20I%20have%20also%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20some%20respect%20for%20donkeys%20that%20are%20considered%20of%20no%20value%20in%20the%20Indian%20setup.%20Besides%2C%20I%20have%20also%20been%20able%20to%20get%20fame%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age.%20Had%20I%20been%20in%20a%20government%20job%2C%20nobody%20would%20have%20known%20of%20my%20existence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dhiren%20Solanki.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716216834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FDhiren-Solanki-1716215826.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donkey%20milk%2C%20which%20has%20little%20value%20in%20India%2C%20has%20made%20Dhiren%20Solanki%20a%20successful%20farmer%20in%20Gujarat.%20He%20tapped%20into%20its%20international%20demand%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20and%20cosmetics%20industry%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20within%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350485%2Fdonkey-milk-farming-value-in-india-gujarat-farmer-earns-lakhs-by-selling-nutritious-donkey-milk-powder%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98MBA%20Sarpanch%E2%80%99%20Who%20Kept%20All%20Her%20Promises%20%26amp%3B%20Brought%20Water%2C%20Roads%20%26amp%3B%20Education%20to%20a%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20lies%20a%20road%20in%20the%20main%20bazaar%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20Soda%20village%20of%20Rajasthan.%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20it%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20ordinary%20village%20street%2C%20but%20the%20locals%20see%20it%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20progress.%20As%20I%20get%20on%20a%20call%20with%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20steady%20sound%20of%20trucks%2C%20cars%2C%20bullock%20carts%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20bicycles%20ploughing%20through%20the%20street%20eclipse%20most%20of%20his%20words.%20He%20shouts%20over%20the%20din%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20trucks%20can%20drive%20on%20this%20road!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20is%20a%20miracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20even%20two%20bicycles%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pass%20simultaneously.%20What%20else%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20a%20two-foot-wide%20road%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks.%20I%20agree.%20So%2C%20naturally%2C%20watching%20the%20path%20accommodating%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20is%20amusing%20for%20the%20villagers.%20The%20farmer%20is%20quick%20to%20hail%20his%20ex-%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20decision-maker%20elected%20by%20the%20village)%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20for%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85603%2Fwomen-sarpanches-transforming-inspiring-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephenomenal%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stresses%20though%20that%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20transformation%20she%20has%20brought%20about.%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20has%20water%20thanks%20to%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Rajawat%20took%20over%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20time%20making%20headlines%20for%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20an%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20the%20village%20was%20experiencing%20one%20of%20its%20worst%20droughts.%20%E2%80%9CMadam%20ensured%20a%20pipeline%20in%20every%20house%20and%20water%20in%20every%20pond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20place%20where%20he%20has%20been%20witnessing%20the%20results%20of%20Rajawat%E2%80%99s%20work.%20His%20fields%20too%20have%20benefited.%20Promising%20to%20send%20me%20pictures%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20pulses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20farmer%20credits%20the%20steady%20supply%20of%20water%20for%20this.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20my%20fields%20would%20dry%20up%20completely.%20But%20not%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20in%20the%20two%20terms%20that%20Rajawat%20headed%20the%20village%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%202010-15%20and%202015-20%2C%20she%20shaped%2C%20both%2C%20policies%20and%20dreams.%20As%20she%20points%20out%2C%20the%20victory%20is%20personal.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20is%20her%20native%20village.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20chasing%20corporate%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20Rajawat%20worked%20for%20a%20slew%20of%20multinational%20companies%20after%20completing%20her%20MBA%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20one%20question%20continued%20to%20baffle%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20government%20funding%20for%20rural%20development%20increasing%20over%20the%20years%2C%20why%20were%20villages%20not%20progressing%3F%20Why%20was%20development%20in%20retreat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversations%20with%20the%20villagers%20led%20her%20to%20the%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20to%20understand%20that%20responsibility%20and%20ownership%20were%20slowly%20regressing%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dindian%2Bvillages%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIJCAEQIRgKGKABMgkIAhAhGAoYoAHSAQg0OTcyajBqNKgCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20landscapes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3C