%20place%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20religious%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ELifestyle%20Asia%20report%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20park%20also%20holds%20a%20significant%20mythological%20association.%20According%20to%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%2C%20it%20is%20the%20place%20where%20Lord%20Hanuman%20found%20the%20magical%20herb%20%E2%80%9CSanjeevani%E2%80%9D%20to%20help%20save%20Lakshman%2C%20brother%20of%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20who%20was%20injured%20during%20the%20battle%20between%20Lord%20Rama%20and%20demon%20King%20Ravana.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reach%20the%20valley%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planning%20a%20trek%20to%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20most%20convenient%20modes%20of%20transportation%20to%20reach%20your%20starting%20point%20at%20Govindghat.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20can%20get%20there%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Car%3A%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20drive%20from%20major%20cities%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20journey%20from%20Delhi%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20traffic%20and%20road%20conditions.%20From%20Delhi%2C%20you%20can%20also%20avail%20public%20transport%20from%20ISBT%20or%20Delhi%20Gate%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20take%20another%20bus%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20then%20to%20Govindghat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ll%20travel%20through%20major%20towns%20such%20as%20Rishikesh%20and%20Haridwar%20before%20reaching%20Govindghat.%20The%20roads%20are%20scenic%2C%20offering%20beautiful%20views%20of%20the%20mountains%20and%20rivers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Air%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearest%20airport%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20Jolly%20Grant%20Airport%20in%20Dehradun.%20From%20the%20airport%2C%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20taxi%20or%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20drive%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20286%20km%20and%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20so%20you%20might%20want%20to%20plan%20your%20flight%20arrival%20time%20accordingly.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYou%20can%20opt%20for%20public%20transport%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20then%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20(%40valleyofflowers)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Rail%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closest%20railway%20station%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20Rishikesh%2C%20which%20is%20well-connected%20to%20major%20cities%20in%20India.%20Once%20you%20arrive%20at%20Rishikesh%2C%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20taxi%20or%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20drive%20from%20Rishikesh%20to%20Govindghat%20takes%20about%2010-11%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20reach%20Govindghat%2C%20you%20can%20begin%20your%20trek%20towards%20Ghangaria%20and%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers.%20Make%20sure%20to%20check%20the%20local%20transportation%20options%20and%20plan%20your%20journey%20ahead%20of%20time%20for%20a%20smooth%20travel%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay-wise%20itinerary%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20to%20travellers%20and%20bloggers%2C%20Himani%20and%20Sagar%20Patel%2C%20who%20travelled%20to%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20in%202019.%20The%20couple%20completed%20the%20trek%20in%205%20days%2C%20slowly%20taking%20in%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20their%20day-wise%20plan-%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%201%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20couple%20drove%20from%20Rishikesh%20to%20Joshimath.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20reached%20Joshimath%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20checked%20into%20a%20local%20guest%20house%20to%20recharge%20ourselves%20for%20the%20upcoming%20trek%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%202%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20trekked%20till%20Ghangharia%20which%20is%20around%209%20km%20from%20the%20starting%20point%20and%20is%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20ft.%20We%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20a%20campsite%20in%20Ghangharia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20serves%20as%20the%20base%20camp%20for%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298559%2Fbest-jungle-camps-wildlife-safaris-india-for-nature-lovers-travel-long-weekend%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20stay%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2