EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20healthy%20food%20space%2C%20the%20founders%20believe%20that%20their%20differentiation%20lies%20in%20the%20transparency%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20products.%20All%20their%20products%20have%20complete%20ingredients%20listed%20behind%20them%20and%20an%20option%20to%20trace%20the%20ingredient%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20farm%20to%20fork%20on%20their%20website%20using%20the%20product%20name%20and%20batch%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20share%20that%20their%20startup%20rests%20on%20four%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTrue%20to%20our%20food%20(nutrition)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20word%20(transparency)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20planet%20(recycle)%2C%20and%20true%20to%20our%20families%20(people).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20completely%20honest%20about%20what%20we%20put%20in%20our%20products%20by%20naming%20it%20all%20on%20the%20pack.%20We%20ensure%20that%20we%20even%20mention%20ingredients%20that%20aren%E2%80%99t%20compulsory%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20stand%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20a%20plastic-neutral%20brand%2C%20wherein%20all%20the%20plastic%20that%20they%20are%20using%20is%20recycled.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20process%20about%2030%20percent%20directly%2C%20while%20we%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20processes%20the%20remaining.%20It%20is%20converted%20into%20biofuel%20and%20supplied%20to%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20Elements%20is%20a%20certified%20%E2%80%98Clean%20Label%E2%80%99%20brand%20by%20the%20Clean%20Label%20Project%2C%20US%2C%20and%20100%20percent%20whole%20grain%20brand%20by%20the%20Whole%20Grains%20Council%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20presence%20built%20around%20300%20towns%20in%20India%20with%20over%20300%20employees%2C%20supplying%20to%20over%20five%20lakh%20households%20every%20month%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20working%20towards%20their%20mission%20of%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nore