rking%20for%20society%20%E2%80%94%20stronger%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Maya%20reflects%20on%20her%20journey%20and%20shares%20what%20led%20her%20to%20this%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20saving%20lives%20became%20her%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20was%20a%20starry-eyed%20child%20who%20dreamt%20of%20doing%20something%20great.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20times%20that%20I%20was%20born%20in%2C%20my%20family%20was%20very%20supportive%20and%20liberal.%20I%20scored%20good%20marks%20on%20the%20school%20board%20exams%20and%20got%20admitted%20to%20medical%20school%20in%20Ajmer%20and%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20grew%20up%20in%20luxury%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20her%20own%20path%20in%20life.%20So%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medical%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20my%20internship%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20husband.%20We%20decided%20to%20get%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20son.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20that%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20pursue%20a%20diploma%20in%20anesthesiology%20because%20it%20was%20a%20career%20that%20I%20could%20manage%20while%20raising%20a%20family.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20completed%20my%20diploma%2C%20I%20had%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20another%20child%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201972%2C%20she%20also%20did%20an%20MS%20in%20anaesthesia.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20giving%20lectures%20on%20anaesthesia%20at%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20Jaipur%20where%20I%20came%20across%20an%20opportunity.%20It%20was%20a%20fellowship%20in%20London%20for%20paediatric%20anaesthesia.%20With%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20attend%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-b