Sawai%20Man%20Singh%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20around%20the%20time%20of%20my%20retirement%20in%201985%20when%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20Academy%20in%20Jaipur%20contacted%20me%20and%20requested%20I%20give%20a%20three-day%20course%20on%20road%20safety%20and%20lifesaving.%20I%20readily%20agreed%20to%20the%20request%2C%20unaware%20that%20it%20would%20shape%20the%20course%20of%20my%20post-retirement%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20was%20very%20successful%20and%20all%20the%20senior%20officers%20posted%20on%20highways%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%20were%20sent%20to%20her%20for%20yet%20another%20course.%20%E2%80%9CA%20photographer%20had%20come%20to%20take%20some%20pictures%20of%20the%20event.%20It%20was%20a%20few%20months%20later%20that%20he%20rang%20me%20up%20and%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20saved%20his%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photographer%20had%20been%20in%20an%20accident%20and%20could%20feel%20bleeding%20in%20his%20inner%20thighs%20and%20back.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20around%20him%20were%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20help%20him%20and%20were%20taking%20pictures%20of%20him.%20He%20explained%20someone%20to%20lift%20him%20and%20put%20him%20in%20a%20certain%20position%20that%20slowed%20the%20bleeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20narrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20timely%20move%20reduced%20the%20blood%20loss%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20the%20photographer%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CHis%20words%20and%20appreciation%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20offering%20such%20courses.%20It%20also%20revealed%20the%20sad%20reality%20of%20the%20state%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India.%20Not%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20in%20the%20crowd%20knew%20lifesaving%20s