am%20from%20Jaipur%20had%20reached%20our%20small%20town.%20I%20was%20keen%20to%20know%20what%20they%20were%20sharing%20and%20had%20to%20try%20it.%20We%20are%20always%20aware%20of%20the%20safety%20threats%20on%20the%20road%20but%20attending%20the%20seminar%20helped%20me%20understand%20what%20can%20be%20done%20to%20save%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20how%20we%20can%20give%20CPR%20and%20first%20aid%20to%20an%20injured%20person.%20We%20were%20also%20given%20instructions%20about%20who%20we%20can%20contact%20for%20help%20if%20a%20person%20needs%20to%20be%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338010%2Fkerala-startup-mykare-building-uber-of-healthcare-for-surgeries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThey%20also%20told%20us%20about%20the%20various%20road%20safety%20rules%20and%20laws%2C%20which%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20existed.%20I%20think%20such%20seminars%20are%20very%20important%20as%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20you%20can%20help%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20bystanders%20during%20an%20accident%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20a%20misconception%20about%20helping%20a%20person%20who%20has%20had%20an%20accident.%20There%20are%20clear%20laws%20that%20save%20the%20bystanders%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20investigation%2C%20but%20there%20are%20not%20many%20people%20who%20know%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20awareness%20brings%20hesitation%20in%20people%20to%20help%20the%20injured%20person%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20mouth%20to%20mouth%20to%20a%20person%20who%20has%20collapsed%2C%20say%20due%20to%20heart%20attack%2C%20giving%20CPR%20can%20save%20their%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20levels%20of%20intervention%20Sahayta%20Trust%20does%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20different%20ways%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20public.%20We%20do%20seminars%20both%20online%20and%20offline%3B%20we%20also%20conduct%20workshops%20and%20classes.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20also%20do%20rallies%20and%20street%20plays%20to%20raise%20awareness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20module%20that%20the%20trust%20follows%20for%20the%20seminars%20and%20courses%20is%20Maya%E2%80%99s%20speciality.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20small%20course%2C%20we%20prioritise%20giving%20them%20the%20instructions%20of%20what%20to%20do%20in%20the%20first%2010%20seconds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCheck%20for%20head%20injuries%20and%20bleeding%3B%20once%20you%20have%20secured%20what%20the%20problem%20is%2C%20you%20can%20act%20accordingly.%20If%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20lungs%20and%20heart%20are%20giving%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F191316%2Fias-hero-inspiring-civil-servants-save-lives-daman-collector-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresorting%20to%20CPR%20is%20the%20best%20way.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%20when%20there%20is%20internal%20bleeding.%20If%20a%20person%20is%20suffering%20from%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20only%20an%20external%20CPR%20can%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20courses%20and%20training%2C%20the%20trust%20also%20works%20with%20government%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20emergency%20services%20in%20public%20places%20like%20malls%20and%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20hurdle%20that%20Maya%20faces%20is%20to%20bring%20people%20to%20attend%20the%20workshops.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20public%20is%20always%20in%20a%20hurry.%20It%20is%20very%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20take%20time%20and%20reach%20us.%20We%20see%20a%20low%20rate%20of%20response%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20keep%20visiting%20our%20courses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20leading%20in%20road%20accidents%20and%20road%20deaths.%20To%20combat%20this%20lack%20of%20response%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20model%20where%20we%20train%20people%2C%20especially%20from%20rural%20areas%2C%20in%20lifesaving.%20And%20then%20they%20reach%20out%20to%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Maya%20has%20trained%20over%201%20lakh%20people%20in%20life%20saving%20and%20road%20safety.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350316%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Maya%20has%20trained%20over%201%20lakh%20people%20in%20life%20saving%20and%20road%20safety.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trust%20provides%20the%20person%20with%20pieces%20of%20equipment%20and%20mannequins%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanjeeva%E2%80%99%20(lifesaver)%2C%20and%20they%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20help%20us%20spread%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dr%20May