0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8448164%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20research%20%3C%2Fa%3Earticle%20points%20out%20that%20these%20mangoes%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20botanically%20classified%20as%20Mangifera%20Indica%20%E2%80%93%20have%20anti-cancer%2C%20anti-inflammatory%2C%20antimicrobial%2C%20antioxidant%2C%20and%20immunomodulatory%20properties.%20Its%20consumption%20may%20potentially%20be%20beneficial%20in%20breast%20cancer%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subrat%20grows%20rare%20plants%20like%20Hydrangea%20and%20world's%20costiliest%20Miyazaki%20mangoes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESubrat%20grows%20rare%20plants%20like%20Hydrangea%20and%20world%E2%80%99s%20costiliest%20Miyazaki%20mangoes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%2C%20Subrat%20came%20home%20with%20the%20sapling%20and%20decided%20to%20grow%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20care%2C%20the%20sapling%20has%20now%20grown%20into%20a%20nine-feet%20tall%20tree